This directory contains a fork of SolveSpace's libslvs library.

ORIGINAL PROJECT INFORMATION:
=============================
Project: SolveSpace
Website: https://solvespace.com
Source: https://github.com/solvespace/solvespace
License: GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPL-3.0)
Copyright: SolveSpace contributors

COMPLIANCE NOTICE:
==================
This fork is created to enable static linking of libslvs with slvsx-cli.
In compliance with GPL-3.0:

1. The complete source code of libslvs is included in this directory
2. All modifications are clearly documented
3. The original copyright notices are preserved
4. This combined work (slvsx-cli + libslvs) is distributed under GPL-3.0

MODIFICATIONS:
==============
The only modifications made to the original SolveSpace code are:
1. Build system changes to enable static library compilation
2. No functionality has been removed or truncated
3. All solver capabilities remain intact

